title: Vilhena (Ernesto Jardim de)
body: He was a deputy for Madeira in the parliamentary session from 1908 to 1910.

Ernesto Jardim de Vilhena: Deputy for Madeira in the parliamentary session from 1908 to 1910.

1908: Ernesto Jardim de Vilhena was a deputy for Madeira.
1910: Ernesto Jardim de Vilhena concluded the mandate as a deputy for Madeira.
